io.amelia.support

Class Version

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.amelia.support.Version
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Version>

    public class Version
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Version>
    Used to compare semantic versioning strings with support for optional release stage and/or build number. e.g., 1.2.3-alpha.1+B001
    See Also:
    "[[http://semver.org/]]"
